@startuml
!include /Users/q284340/Agentic/coding/docs/puml/_standard-style.puml

title Health Monitoring & Dashboard System - Interaction Flow

participant "User" as U
participant "Dashboard Web UI" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Health Monitor Service" as HMS
participant "Metrics Collector" as MC
participant "Data Store" as DS
participant "Alert Manager" as AM
participant "Notification Service" as NS

U -> UI: Access Health Dashboard
activate UI

UI -> GW: Request System Status
activate GW

GW -> HMS: Get Health Metrics
activate HMS

HMS -> MC: Collect Current Metrics
activate MC

MC -> DS: Query Health Data
activate DS
DS --> MC: Return Metrics Data
deactivate DS

MC --> HMS: Aggregated Metrics
deactivate MC

HMS -> HMS: Analyze Health Status

alt Critical Issue Detected
    HMS -> AM: Trigger Alert
    activate AM
    AM -> NS: Send Notification
    activate NS
    NS -> U: Alert Notification
    deactivate NS
    deactivate AM
end

HMS --> GW: Health Status Response
deactivate HMS

GW --> UI: System Status Data
deactivate GW

UI -> UI: Render Dashboard View
UI --> U: Display Health Dashboard
deactivate UI

loop Continuous Monitoring (Every 30s)
    MC -> DS: Collect New Metrics
    MC -> HMS: Update Health Status
    HMS -> UI: Push Real-time Updates
end

note right of HMS
Pattern Significance: 6/10
Occurrences: 12
Trend: Increasing
end note

@enduml